<item>
            <title>[PDFBOX-5135] Glyphs missed in rendering</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-5135</link>
                <project id="12310760" key="PDFBOX">PDFBox</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Hi Team&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We have found a PDF that can&apos;t be rendered correctly in PDFBox. It renders correctly in Adobe and Poppler.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;PDFs could not be uploaded so I&apos;ve added them to a google drive folder. If that doesn&apos;t work please tell me and provide a way to send them.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1mddhI_rpvyNojj4MKMyunRBrBOQe54HF?usp=sharing&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1mddhI_rpvyNojj4MKMyunRBrBOQe54HF?usp=sharing&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Best regards&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Daniel&lt;/p&gt;</description>
