                            <comment id="17304291" author="tilman" created="Thu, 18 Mar 2021 17:03:14 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;re the log message (&quot;GlyphDescription for index 2 is null, returning 0&quot;):&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;components has 3 elements, descriptions has only 2 keys: 372, 43. Third key (2) is missing.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Another weirdness is that simpleglyph 372 has a one contour, 2 has none (which may be the reason). Image from DTL OTMaster 3.7 light:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;image-wrap&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/attachment/13022605/13022605_image-2021-03-18-18-02-17-417.png&quot; style=&quot;border: 0px solid black&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17304398" author="tilman" created="Thu, 18 Mar 2021 19:51:36 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The cause is in GlyphTable.getGlyph(), that one returns null for &quot;no outline&quot;. This glyph is then missed in GlyfCompositeDescript.initDescriptions(). I&apos;m now generating an empty glyph and the files render properly. I&apos;ll commit the changes on the weekend.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17304413" author="kalaspuffar" created="Thu, 18 Mar 2021 20:07:29 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Hi Tilman.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Great work, but I guess this will not be in the upcoming release?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Best regards&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Daniel&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17304429" author="tilman" created="Thu, 18 Mar 2021 20:28:05 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;No, that&apos;s too late. The release had already been packaged and will probably go out tomorrow.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17305148" author="jira-bot" created="Fri, 19 Mar 2021 19:27:17 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Commit 1887822 from Tilman Hausherr in branch &apos;pdfbox/branches/2.0&apos;&lt;br/&gt;
[ &lt;a href=&quot;https://svn.apache.org/r1887822&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://svn.apache.org/r1887822&lt;/a&gt; ]&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-5135&quot; title=&quot;Glyphs missed in rendering&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PDFBOX-5135&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PDFBOX-5135&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: don&apos;t ignore glyphs with 0 contours because these may be used by composite glyphs&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17305149" author="jira-bot" created="Fri, 19 Mar 2021 19:27:20 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Commit 1887823 from Tilman Hausherr in branch &apos;pdfbox/trunk&apos;&lt;br/&gt;
[ &lt;a href=&quot;https://svn.apache.org/r1887823&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://svn.apache.org/r1887823&lt;/a&gt; ]&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-5135&quot; title=&quot;Glyphs missed in rendering&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PDFBOX-5135&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PDFBOX-5135&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: don&apos;t ignore glyphs with 0 contours because these may be used by composite glyphs&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17305156" author="jira-bot" created="Fri, 19 Mar 2021 19:42:31 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Commit 1887824 from Tilman Hausherr in branch &apos;pdfbox/trunk&apos;&lt;br/&gt;
[ &lt;a href=&quot;https://svn.apache.org/r1887824&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://svn.apache.org/r1887824&lt;/a&gt; ]&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-5135&quot; title=&quot;Glyphs missed in rendering&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PDFBOX-5135&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PDFBOX-5135&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: remove method that isn&apos;t used (and doesn&apos;t contain the bugfix); simplify API&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17305169" author="tilman" created="Fri, 19 Mar 2021 20:08:01 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Re the deprecated / deleted method - it&apos;s not used, and doing the bugfix isn&apos;t that difficult, but it would be difficult to test it because the method isn&apos;t used. But if anybody outside PDFBox uses it, please come forward, I would then find a way to test it, e.g. open the font twice, get the glyphs with both methods and compare.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17305170" author="tilman" created="Fri, 19 Mar 2021 20:08:25 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I&apos;m done. Thanks for the report!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
